               <occupation type="ruler">Emperor</occupation>

               <floruit when="1494">He was the son of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3874eskender">
                     <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe</roleName>
                   ʾƎskǝndǝr</persName>,
                  crowned in <date>1494</date> at the age of seven or even younger.
                  His short reign of only six or seven months was characterized by continued civil war and bloodshed,
                  with one faction at the court favouring him and another his uncle
                  <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7481NaodA">
                     <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe</roleName>
                      Nāʿod (ʾAnbasā Baḍar)</persName>.
